Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been tall ever since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When we line up for morning assembly, I'm always at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I happen to be named "Koizumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "Oizumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone needs to watch their health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the third-years, who will need to prepare for exams soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The first-years should be careful, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My summon monsters have all been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:16.71,Title,,0,0,0,,Freshman year summer! \NI'll definitely find a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.08,Superscript,,0,0,0,,So you stayed up all night playing games, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not very lady-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And sleeping while standing? \NAre you a giraffe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have been one in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the joker, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, since you think you're so funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...as punishment you'll come to school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Summer vacation starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:30.56,Overlap,,0,0,0,,You don't get a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to take summer classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huuuuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that "huh." That's it. Now get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Being tall has absolutely no advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do, I always draw attention to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been trying really hard on the basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're great Kotani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My name.... is Otani, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, you amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being kind and helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you turn around and call me an amazon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I could call you Kyoshinhei instead…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, All Hanshin-Kyojin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hanshin-Kyojin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time Nakano-sensei called us that was on the first day of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does no one want to be class representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about All Hanshin-Kyojin over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have Koizumi and Otani do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! I'm trying to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, you amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who should move, midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. The lovers spat ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,These summer classes are such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan, you failed the midterm test so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my darling is going to school for basketball practice anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakao-kun, huh? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, if I only had a boyfriend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, at the very least, just someone I like. \NThen I would be more motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure are weird, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually signed up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from the top student of our grade. You sure think differently from the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want to feel left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard that during summer classes all the different classes are grouped together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there'll be any nice guys there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I won't have to see that midget Otani, it'll be heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like guys that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to ask the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget that Otani is a dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here because I snored during the graduation ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I didn't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Snoring is so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hanshin-Kyojin, will you perform your comedy routine over the summer, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan, switch seats with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... sitting next to a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the worst summer ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there'll be any nice guys there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't taken attendance yet. \NYou're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with Class 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Abe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Omaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I sit behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sit behind Koizumi, you won't be able to see the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm a little tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this'll be the best summer ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dreamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you walk home with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a delinquent, midget?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I hang out with you after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have something important to say that I can't say here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How weird... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...like guys like Suzuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are easy to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.69,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.69,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Love at first sight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to blackmail me for cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a super good guy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happens that I intend to become friends with Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to set you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a decent guy after all, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You only just realized now, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you were someone who bore a grudge against giraffes in his past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this thing about giraffes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's on me, so order whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A jumbo burger, a fish burger, or a super value set meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A super value set meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Chiharu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeeeeeeeh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So Chiharu-chan is your type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot? She's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From a girl's point of view, I suppose she is kind of cute but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess short people like other short people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have to tell you something unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan dislikes guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if she doesn't like guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cure her of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I'll give it my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir, we don't allow shadow boxing in here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yea… Nakao-chi and I are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... a friend of mine will be coming, too. \NThat's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A pool can make you that happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to the pool for a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither! Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really different from the school pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! I was so happy, I lost sight of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be you didn't really want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't, I wouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys seem interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun, are you attending summer classes because you failed the midterm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I had a cold the day of the test, so I couldn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A topic... I need to find a topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But I have no idea what to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play beach volleyball, the four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You call standing around in the water and not doing anything fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just because you're trying to pretend to be nice a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what you normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.43,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where did Nakao-kun and Nobu-chan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them went over there a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To the water slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Slide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun, let's go on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.02,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san, lets go on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if we go play for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Water slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down! And don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! We did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where's Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He's been gone for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He went somewhere when I met up with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She left me all alone and ran off to play with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit thirsty, so I went to get some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are thoughtful, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a warm drink for you, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you seemed cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Should I have gotten you a warm drink too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You went on that a lot of times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was super fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can talk with him normally now. \NThis is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure got tanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, right? I tan really quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan doesn't seem to dislike guys anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun's houses are in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And Chiharu doesn't dislike guys anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She and I were pretty lovey-dovey, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you guys seemed to be getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a pretty good mood going on too, Koizuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all thanks to you, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's work hard again tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's reach for happiness together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,....I was still filled with an indescribable feeling of dread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun sure is a nice guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've fallen for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, no. That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He walked me home yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He walked you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought that guys were brutish and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But Suzuki-kun is very kind. \NHe's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were getting along well with Otani yesterday, Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said, Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really easy to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because he's short, so he doesn't seem like a guy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani... You're sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man that was harsh. If Otani had heard that, what would he—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Otani…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday sure was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are funny, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am small, therefore I am Kotani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kotani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell the teacher that Kotani will be absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:00.51,Overlap,,0,0,0,,It's "Otani."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to call me Kotani, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to comfort me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I was just worried about you. What's with that sarcastic attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's being sarcastic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if you got called small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm small so I don't count as a guy—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Big or small, as long as you have a **** you're a man, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls shouldn't say that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you always been called small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like this just because a girl said it is pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get so depressed over stuff like this, no one will ever like you, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.. {Pisses me off...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. That idiot's punch really woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Class has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at getting up early in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't get up early in the winter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for yesterday. I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, Tanaka-san seemed scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun sure is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.... she's just not comfortable around guys. It's not your fault, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...for some reason, I find you easy to talk with, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because we're almost the same height,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I don't think of you as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So Tanaka-san doesn't hate me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me... you like Chiharu-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just hot. Very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He definitely likes her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That look totally gave it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were smacking me just a minute ago. \NWhat are you so depressed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, just forget about what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I normally pretend to not care,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it really hurts when it's coming from the person I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's payback for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.74,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up on Chiharu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get so depressed over stuff like this, no one will ever like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were my grandpa's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're here, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd been alone, who knows where I'd have to run off too and hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep trying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani invited Chiharu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for my sexy yukata seduction plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't look right on a tall woman like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan and the others aren't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The train was packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that maybe they got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize you for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit me at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you really went all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, I was late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's here, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bumped into him on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To prevent her from getting bumped, he switched positions with her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear... It's clear, but it's clearly upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They look pretty good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like a couple who have just started going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels like the ending of the comedy show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Risa-chan? Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Waah! It broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Otani, next we'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so short. I thought you got lost in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say that? \NThat was pretty awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get some grilled cuttlefish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani might be small,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...but his hand still feels like a guy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We may always be fighting, but our personalities kind of suit each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we both have height complexes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you. Please go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that, Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun became a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I feel better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Chiharu-chan looked pretty good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you and Suzuki-kun didn't work out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can find a girlfriend quickly enough if I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh is that so? I'd like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who can get someone faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I get if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you whatever game you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I win, you'll buy me a new pair of basketball shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! An ex-girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Otani's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: The Ex-Girlfriend Love Triangle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.98,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,The Ex-Girlfriend Love Triangle!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
